data.description: Horse Property, corrals,1762 sq ft metal barn, 4 stalls, tack room, large hay storage, 60' round pen, 5 fenced steel pastures w/ gates water & electric. 486 sq ft workshop, House Remodeled 2019. This is a Farm, Ranch style.home with 2752 sq ft, Great Room w/rock front, wood burning fireplace additional desk area in living room area. 3 bedrooms 3 baths, newly remodeled kitchen, Alder knotty pine cabinets, upgraded appliances, all electric home. Upstairs 2 bedrooms, 1 bath, Loft area plus bonus rooms ,1 bathroom. ETS electric heat, 3 car garage, abundance of storage.  360-degree views of the Greer mountains, USFS surrounds property.  Walk out of your home, go riding into the sunset. Horse lovers dream. Within walking distance of Greer Village, Colorado River, Hiking, Fishing at Greer Lake
